<Body><Title>四川攀枝花地震已部分房屋垮塌</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2008年8月30日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">新华网成都</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">8月30日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">电</Denoter></Event>  （记者肖林、杨三军） </Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e2" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s2">记者</Participant>从攀枝花仁和区和凉山彝族自治州会理县<Denoter  type="perception" did="d2">了解</Denoter>到</Event>，
			<Event eid="e3"><Time type="relTime" tid="t3">30日16时30分</Time>在<Location lid="l3">两地交界处</Location>发生的6.1级<Denoter type="emergency" did="d3">地震</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e4">已造成部分乡镇<Object oid="o4,o5">房屋</Object><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d4">垮塌</Denoter></Event>、
			<Event eid="e5"><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d5">扯裂</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event polarity="negative" eid="e6">尚未<Denoter type="action" did="d6">接到</Denoter>人员伤亡<Object oid="o6">报告</Object></Event>。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>
    
　　<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e7" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s7">记者</Participant>从仁和区委和会理县值班室电话联系<Denoter type="perception" did="d7">获悉</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e8"><Location lid="l8">两地城区</Location><Denoter type="emergency" did="d8">震感</Denoter>明显</Event>，
			<Event eid="e9">但无<Object oid="o9">房屋</Object><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d9">倒塌</Denoter></Event>。
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e10"><Participant sid="s10">震区人员</Participant>已<Denoter type="movement" did="d9">跑</Denoter>出<Location type="origin" lid="l9">住房</Location></Event>，
			<Event eid="e11"><Participant sid="s10">当地政府</Participant>正在组织<Denoter type="operation" did="d10">抢险</Denoter></Event></Sentence>。<Sentence>因地震造成
			<Event eid="e12"><Object oid="o12">通讯</Object><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d12">障碍</Denoter></Event>，当地大多乡镇仍然联系不上。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e13" type="thoughtevent">据<Participant sid="s13">仁和区委值班室值班人员</Participant><Denoter  type="statement" did="d12">介绍</Denoter></Event>，该区平地镇反映，
			<Event eid="e14"><Location lid="l14">镇上</Location>已出现<Object oid="o14,o15">房屋</Object><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d13">倒塌</Denoter></Event>、
			<Event eid="e15"><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d15">扯裂</Denoter>现象</Event>。
			<Event polarity="negative" eid="e16">没有<Denoter type="action" did="d16">接到</Denoter>人员伤亡<Object oid="o16">报告</Object></Event>。
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
			其他乡镇一直打不进电话。
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
			估计灾情较重的应是大龙潭乡和平地镇。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e17" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s17">记者</Participant>从攀枝花市仁和区有关部门<Denoter  type="perception" did="d17">了解</Denoter>到</Event>，
			<Event eid="e18"><Time type="timeInterval" tid="t18">到18时12分</Time>，<Location lid="l18">当地</Location>至少发生二三次有明显震感的<Denoter type="emergency" did="d18">余震</Denoter>，</Event>
				<Event eid="e19">沿<Location lid="l19">金沙江一带</Location>估计有<Object oid="o19">房屋</Object><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d19">倒塌</Denoter></Event>和
			<Event eid="e20"><Participant sid="s20">人员</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d20">伤亡</Denoter></Event>。
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
			当地重灾乡镇为大龙潭乡、平地镇，因电话不通，
			<Event eid="e21"><Participant sid="s21">仁和区委、区政府领导</Participant>已<Denoter type="movement" did="d21">赶赴</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l21">这两个乡镇</Location></Event>。
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event polarity="negative" eid="e22">区委所在地<Location lid="l22">仁和镇</Location>暂未<Denoter type="perception" did="d22">发现</Denoter><Object>房屋倒塌和人员伤亡</Object></Event>。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e23">据<Participant sid="s23">会理县政府值班室人员</Participant><Denoter  type="statement" did="d23">介绍</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e24"><Participant sid="s24">该县</Participant>已<Denoter type="operation" did="d24">联系</Denoter>上<Participant oid="o24">江竹乡</Participant></Event>，
			<Event eid="e25"><Object oid="o25">该乡学校房屋</Object>在地震中<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d25">扯裂</Denoter></Event>，
			其他乡镇也因通讯障碍无法联系上。
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
			估计灾情会出现在沿金沙江的一些乡镇。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>
	</Content>
